sentences.sentence: The document will be circulated to all members.
sentences.translation: 这份文件将在所有成员中传阅。

sentences.sentence: The text of his recent speech was circulated among leading republicans.
sentences.translation: 他新近演讲的文字稿在共和党领导人之间传阅。

sentences.sentence: The document was previously circulated in New York at the United Nations.
sentences.translation: 这份文件过去曾在纽约的联合国总部传阅过。
